</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="hero">
                    <img src="~/image/bgimg.jpg" alt="Background Image">
                    <div class="hero-text">
                        <h1>Welcome to Our E-commerce Store</h1>
                        <p>Discover the best deals on a wide range of products!</p>
                        <form class=" " asp-controller="Home" asp-action="CallAPi" data-ajax="true" data-ajax-method="GET" data-ajax-begin="onBeginapi" data-ajax-success="onSuccessapi" data-ajax-failure="onFailureapi">
                        <button type="submit" style="display:flex;">Predict AQI</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="main-content">
                <div class="product">
                    <div class="product-image">
                        <img src="~/image/airnew1.jpg" alt="Product Image">
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-description">
                        <h2>Product Title</h2>
                        <p> Breathe easier with PureAir Pro. Our advanced air purifier utilizes cutting-edge technology to eliminate airborne contaminants,ensuring clean and healthy indoor air. Experience freshness in every breath with PureAir Pro.</p>
                        <p class="price">$99.99</p>
                        <button>Add to Cart</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="reviews">
                <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
                <div class="review">
                    <div class="customer">
                        <img src="~/image/cr2.jpeg" alt="Customer 1" class="customer-img">
                        <p class="customer-name">John Doe</p>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-text">"I've noticed a significant improvement in air quality since using PureAir Pro. It's whisper-quiet and incredibly effective. Highly recommend!"</p>
                </div>
                <div class="review">
                    <div class="customer">
                        <img src="~/image/cr1.jpeg" alt="Customer 2" class="customer-img">
                        <p class="customer-name">Jane Smith</p>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-text">"PureAir Pro has made a noticeable difference in my home. My allergies have improved, and I no longer wake up congested. Thank you for this amazing product!"</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Add more reviews as needed -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
